<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạltsbyḥ bylyq bjlạlk wạlạ̉sẖwạq klhạ rạyḥạlk
 wạlạ̉dẖhạn wlạ ywm tnsạlk ʿẓmẗ ạ̹ydk fy ạlạ̉ʿmạl

[V2]
 kl ạlkwn wyạ ạlmskwnẗ wạlạ̉rḍ lḥbk mdywnẗ

[V3]
 dy mḥbẗ qlbk mḍmwnẗ lạ bttgẖyr wlạ ttsẖạl

[V4]
 ạlqrạr - kl ạlfrḥ ạ̹n ạ̹ḥnạ kẖlyqtk sr wjwdnạ ndẖyʿ tsbyḥk

[V5]
 wạ̹rạdtk lynạ wmsẖyỷtk nmlạ ạlkwn ạ̉ngẖạm tsạbyḥk

[V6]
 2- lmạ nfkr ạ̹yh hạ nqwl nlqy̱ lsạnnạ fạḍ ʿlṭwl

[V7]
 sẖkr wḥmd wsbḥ yṭwl wf syrtk tḥly̱ htạfạtnạ

[V8]
 wlsạnnạ yktb bmhạrẗ wytrjm ạ̉sẖwạq mḥtạrẗ

[V9]
 wyqdmlk ạ̉ḥly̱ ʿbạrẗ wyfḍl wṣfk fwq ʿbạrạtnạ

[V10]
 3- wbtsbyḥnạ nsẖbʿ qlbk wqlwbnạ tsẖbʿ mn ḥubk

[V11]
 myĩztnạ wbqynạ mn sẖʿbk wjhk bysyr wyryḥnạ

[V12]
 f nhạrnạ tyjy bsḥạbẗ wf lylnạ nạrk mtsạbẗ

[V13]
 fy ạlḥyrẗ tbqạlnạ ạ̹jạbẗ wbthdynạ wbtfrḥnạ

[V14]
 4- ạ̹smk fwq kl ạlạ̉smạʾ tkẖḍʿlk kl ạlạ̉sẖyạʾ

[V15]
 qạdr tṣnʿ ạ̉ḥly̱ ạ̹nạʾ mn ạ̉ʿẓm kẖạṭy wsẖryr

[V16]
 mạ byṣʿbsẖ ʿlyk ṣuʿwbạt wmkẖạrjk ḥty̱ fy mmạt

[V17]
 wtgẖyãr lynạ ạlạ̉wqạt mạ ạlqdrẗ fy ạ̹ydk yạ qdyr</lyrics>
<title>ạltsbyḥ bylyq bjlạlk</title>
</song>